column5: Hi Everyone Just new to the area and looking to try out Wasi lake.  Wondering where I could launch my boat from and a few hints as well.  THanks for any help.
Arty,  PM board member LUCG. He'll help you out with the launch info. It's up to him if he wants to share his secrets.
hey  i know where a couple launches are n the lake, pm me and i will get you the details  cheers!
